    for (int i = 0; i < x.length; i++) {
        sum += Math.abs(x[i] - y[i]);
    }
    return sum;
}
```

3. Chebyshev Distance:

```java
public static double chebyshevDistance(double[] x, double[] y) {
    double max = 0.0;
    for (int i = 0; i < x.length; i++) {
        double diff = Math.abs(x[i] - y[i]);
        if (diff > max) {
            max = diff;
        }
    }
    return max;
}
```

